11. SC Internacional      3  10   0   3   7   8  32 -24   eliminated
Portuguesa, AA das Palmeiras and Brás were tied in 7th position. One tie-breaking tournament was realized to decide which team would be eliminated:

12/10/1924 Portuguesa 3 x 2 AA das Palmeiras
19/10/1924 Brás 2 x 0 AA das Palmeiras
26/10/1924 Brás 5 x 5 Portuguesa 
1. Brás              3 
1. Portuguesa        3
----------------------- 
3. AA das Palmeiras  0 eliminated
As oito primeiras equipes classificaram-se para o Segundo Turno.

